  "text": [
    "If it please God,",
    "let less happen.",
    "Even out Earth's",
    "rondure, flatten",
    "Eiger, blanden",
    "the Grand Canyon.",
    "Make valleys",
    "slightly higher,",
    "widen fissures",
    "to arable land,",
    "remand your",
    "terrible glaciers",
    "and silence",
    "their calving,",
    "halving or doubling",
    "all geographical features",
    "toward the mean.",
    "Unlean against our hearts.",
    "Withdraw your grandeur",
    "from these parts."
  ],
  "title": "Blandeur",
  "year": ""
}